data.description: Welcome to your new home in Liberty, SC. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is the epitome of comfortable living with a covered front porch that is perfect for drinking your morning coffee or enjoying the cool fall evenings on a little over half an acre . Highly desirable lot with most being level and a creek in the back wooded area. The storage building, treehouse, & dollhouse convey with the sale of the home. The Master has a huge walk in closet & on suite bath. Sold As-is. A must see! Seller will credit buyer $5,000 towards closing costs with acceptable offer.
